most valued charities.

83
00:03:00,481 --> 00:03:02,981
- Oh, this better not be
another scheme, Jack.

84
00:03:02,983 --> 00:03:04,323
- You think this is a move?

85
00:03:04,318 --> 00:03:06,318
- Now why would I ever
think that after you tried

86
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:09,760
