times in the last ten minutes?

87
00:03:09,757 --> 00:03:11,387
- I did try
to take over from you.

88
00:03:11,392 --> 00:03:14,162
But I've been at this firm
my entire career,

89
00:03:14,161 --> 00:03:15,731
and I am fighting for it now.

90
00:03:15,729 --> 00:03:17,529
- And you think I'm not?
- I'm sure you are.

91
00:03:17,531 --> 00:03:19,701
But you're also the reason
I'm holding this indictment

92
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,900
