- You know what.

109
00:04:05,079 --> 00:04:07,249
It's time we give that woman
a taste of her own medicine.

110
00:04:07,248 --> 00:04:08,808
- What the hell is that
supposed to mean?

111
00:04:08,816 --> 00:04:10,746
- It means we hire a lawyer
from an outside firm,

112
00:04:10,751 --> 00:04:12,681
and we dig up dirt on someone
she cares about.

113
00:04:12,686 --> 00:04:14,846
- Are you out of your mind?
- You saw what she did to Donna.

114
00:04:14,855 --> 00:04:16,785
It's only a matter of time
before she tries to pull

115
