the same shit with Rachel.
- Mike--

116
00:04:18,292 --> 00:04:19,962
- Harvey, you're the one
that taught me that when someone

117
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:21,730
puts pressure on you,
you put it back on them.

118
00:04:21,729 --> 00:04:23,559
- I also taught you if you're
gonna take a swing at someone,

119
00:04:23,564 --> 00:04:25,804
you better knock them out,
and if we pull the shit

120
00:04:25,799 --> 00:04:27,469
that you're talking about
and get caught,

121
00:04:27,468 --> 00:04:30,238
all that happens is
I get thrown off this case,

122
00:04:30,237 --> 00:04:32,237
and it's game over.

123
00:04:32,239 --> 00:04:34,139
- Harvey, I can't stand by
and watch while the people

124
00:04:34,141 --> 00:04:36,211
I care about get attacked,
and neither could you.

125
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:37,540
- Mike, I promise you,

126
00:04:37,544 --> 00:04:39,444
I will be there for Rachel
every step of the way.

127
00:04:39,446 --> 00:04:40,806
In the meantime,

128
00:04:40,814 --> 00:04:43,384
I need you going through
every one of those boxes.

129
00:04:43,384 --> 00:04:45,284
Because if that woman
is ready to go to trial,

130
00:04:45,286 --> 00:04:47,046
she's got a lot more
than an e-mail

131
00:04:47,054 --> 00:04:49,624
