- I'm not talking about

182
00:06:49,877 --> 00:06:51,777
the University
of Arizona, Louis.

183
00:06:51,779 --> 00:06:54,779
I'm talking about Columbia,
Yale, Stanford--

184
00:06:54,782 --> 00:06:57,282
