241
00:08:56,803 --> 00:08:58,803
that she is putting together
to make her case.

242
00:08:58,805 --> 00:09:00,235
We find them,
we know specifically

243
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,610
what we have to fight.

244
00:09:01,608 --> 00:09:05,338
- And what specifically might
those things look like?

245
00:09:05,345 --> 00:09:09,105
- Witness lists, interviews,
anything to do with Lola Jensen,

246
00:09:09,116 --> 00:09:11,316
utility bills from when I was
supposed to be at Harvard--

247
00:09:11,318 --> 00:09:13,118
- Wait, wait, wait.
Slow down.

248
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,520
- Why are you writing this down?
- So I can remember it.

249
00:09:15,522 --> 00:09:17,792
And because we need a system.

250
00:09:17,791 --> 00:09:20,331
- And because you've never done
doc review before.

251
00:09:21,461 --> 00:09:22,591
I don't believe it.

252
00:09:22,596 --> 00:09:24,126
How you've been a legal
secretary this long,

253
00:09:24,131 --> 00:09:26,231
and never have done doc review.
