if I think it's a good idea

398
00:14:54,794 --> 00:14:58,064
for them to work at Pearson
Specter Litt, and I don't.

399
00:14:58,064 --> 00:15:01,234
- Sheila--
- Louis.

400
00:15:01,234 --> 00:15:03,534
Please don't ask me
to lie to them.

401
00:15:10,477 --> 00:15:11,907
- What are you doing?

402
00:15:11,912 --> 00:15:13,582
- I'm just wondering
if you're gonna stay in here

403
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:14,810
going over stuff all day.

404
00:15:14,814 --> 00:15:16,714
- What else would I be doing?
