00:18:13,259 --> 00:18:14,759
- It's a motion
to have you sanctioned

479
00:18:14,761 --> 00:18:16,431
for improperly
contacting a witness.

480
00:18:16,429 --> 00:18:18,129
- I didn't improperly
contact anyone.

